my miracle.

01:16.462 --> 01:19.158
My wife, Marjorie.

01:19.889 --> 01:22.951
I fell in love with her
the moment I met her.

01:22.951 --> 01:26.167
We both had the love for the Lord.

01:26.167 --> 01:30.103
