my wife, Marjorie.

01:40.008 --> 01:41.177
YOUR HUSBAND IS THE DEVIL

01:41.177 --> 01:43.190
She asked me to pray for a man.

01:43.190 --> 01:46.018
A very intelligent man,
a genius probably,

01:46.018 --> 01:50.003
whose teenage son is
so intellectually disabled,

01:50.003 --> 01:53.428
that he can no longer bear
the burden of raising him.

01:53.428 --> 01:56.685
All the intelligence in the world
would not help this man.

01:56.685 --> 01:59.139
This man needs to pray to God,

01:59.139 --> 02:03.086
to accept God's will,
to heal him.

02:03.383 --> 02:05.240
God's will?

02:05.240 --> 02:07.678
Healing power?

02:08.241 --> 02:12.795
Genetic mutations can not be
healed through prayer.

02:12.795 --> 02:17.376
If inflicting unbearable pain
is how your God test faith,

02:17.376 --> 02:20.867
then he's a vindictive son of a bitch.

